item.description:
Who were you before you were born?

No, we are not talking about past lives. Who were you while you were waiting to be born?

Based upon the work of Helen Wambach, PhD. and utilizing self-hypnosis, this seminar leads you to access prenatal memories and explore the reasons why you chose to be born to live now, as witness to and participant in the great changes happening upon the earth.

Enjoy a group regression session with Kathryn McGlynn, Certified Hypnotist and Time Traveler. Discover answers to many of the questions you may have about your life and life purpose.

Bring a pillow, mat and blanket, if desired.

BONUS: Free hypnosis CD included.

 

Must preregister directly with Heaven on Earth.

For more details: http://www.createheaven.com/index.php/angels/calendar/

or visit http://localendar.com/public/km
